{"tid":1120012,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Nat3 轉 Nat2","createTime":"2019-04-22T10:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T12:08:00.000Z","uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c00feadff12f69a82363b259f884d50525200ecb","tid":1120012,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n本身屋企wifi太慢 所以買左個sim卡router俾ps4用<br />\n但出黎連線係nat3 上網睇教學都整唔到做返nat2<br />\n有冇巴打可以教一教點set up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb0ed65878c143e69f44cb54baa3bc754d30e6d","tid":1120012,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad732432ad0e9558717afc132474d4aae4dcb32f","tid":1120012,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cd3bc2a36c316ff16e0ac20ee122bb3780a7e8","tid":1120012,"uid":247900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"NAT 1的玩家/用戶使用的是乙太網路線，也就是有線網路，根據PSN的官方說法是有開啟DMZ(非軍事區)、連線中間不經過防火牆和路由器。<br />\nNAT 2的玩家/用戶使用的是無線網路<br />\nNAT 3的玩家/用戶使用的是手機熱點"}]}